## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Purpose of the Document

This document outlines the data retention policy for qTest Manager, a test management software developed and maintained by [Your Company]. The purpose of this policy is to define the principles, procedures, and guidelines for the retention and handling of user information within the application.

### 1.2 Scope of the Data Retention Policy

This policy applies to all aspects of user information within qTest Manager. It encompasses data collection, storage, deletion, and archiving processes. The policy is designed to ensure compliance with relevant data protection laws and industry standards.

